hamid karzai   ( pashto/persian : حامد کرزی ; born 24 december 1957 ) served as president of afghanistan for almost ten years , from 7 december 2004 to 29 september 2014 .

follow the leader : a june 2002 grand council known as a loya jirga installed hamid karzai as the president of this embattled country

